column2: She wolf - maquette. The maquette of the She Wolf which served as a symbol of the production. The She Wolf is the traditional symbol of Rome because in legend the two founders of Rome (Romulus and Remus) were nursed by a female wolf. Using the She Wolf as a symbol in Les Troyens was a subtle reminder of the Roman imperative.. Mixed Media. 13'  H x 17'  W x 4 1/4'  D
